開始進行5樓的搜索

7
00:00:27,527 --> 00:00:29,263
Reality slips far away

8
00:00:29,329 --> 00:00:31,165
Fiction comes alive
as we start to play

9
00:00:31,231 --> 00:00:32,866
hope is no more behind a closed door

10
