hope and hopelessness become one

12
00:00:36,770 --> 00:00:38,806
it's all meaningless
we've already begun

13
00:00:38,872 --> 00:00:40,607
we are all one in the same

14
00:00:40,673 --> 00:00:42,710
never opposites
when we play the same game

15
00:00:42,776 --> 00:00:44,511
We walk a thin line
between hope and despair

16
00:00:44,577 --> 00:00:46,313
Running from the truth but
it's already here

17
00:00:46,379 --> 00:00:48,082
Told so many lies I don't know
if they can find me

18
00:00:48,148 --> 00:00:50,184
Only one life to live so choose wisely

19
00:00:50,250 --> 00:00:51,986
Heads or tails Do you even
know what side you're on

20
